HOW THE BULLET LANGUAGE WILL WORK

ex:

//set: sets a value
set direction 15

//values:
direction, speed, size, x, y

//delay: delay for milliseconds
delay 1000

//make: makes a bullet with speed direction
make energyorb 10 90

//effect: play effect
effect flashscreen

//loop:
loop 4,make energyorb 10 90,modify 5 10

//add: add to a value
add direction 10